IBAMBA likaMkhulumeli kahulumeni uNkk Phumla Williams lithi likholwa ukuthi obenguMengameli wakuleli uMnuz Jacob Zuma wayemvikela lowo owayenguNgqongqoshe wezokuXhumana uNksz Faith Muthambi. UNkk Williams uveze lokhu ngesikhathi ethula ubufakazi bakhe kwiKhomishina ephenya ngokugwamandwa kwamandla ombuso.  "Ngicabanga ukuthi uZuma wayemvikela uNksz Muthambi, angazi ukuthi kungani ngaphandle kokuthi kukhona imisebeni abayisusa kumina, bebezenzela umathanda lapha, bayazi ukuthi bengingeke ngiyivume lento abebeyenza yingakho banginqinda amandla," kusho uNkk Williams. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
    supports HTML5 video This is a modal window. Beginning of dialog window. Escape will cancel and close the window. End of dialog window. Uthe impatho kaNksz Muthambi yamkhumbuza ukuhlukumezeka adlula kukho ngesikhathi eyisishoshovu se-ANC ngeminyaka yobandlululo kuleli. Uthe okwamphatha kabi kakhulu ngalokhu ukuthi uZuma wayazi ngendlela uMuthambi ayemphatha ngayo kodwa ekenzanga lutho. “Okubuhlungu ukuthu umengameli Zuma wayazi ngobuhlungu engadlula kubo. Wazi kahle ngobuhlungu bokuhlukunyezwa. Ngakho angiqondi ukuthi kungani athula wangangenelela. Ngangihlukunyezwa, kubahlekisa bona bethi ‘ya sesimqondisile,” kuqhuba uNkk Williams. Uthe ukuhlukunyezwa kwakhe uNksz Muthambi kwenza ukuthi abenokhwantalala. Ohola ubufakazi kulekhomishini, umemezele ukuthi abaphenyi bekhomishini baphenya ngezinsolo zokuthi uMnuz Mwanele Manyi uthumelele uNkk Williams iSMS ngesikhathi ethula ubufakazi. Politics Hub